  "title": "Mechanic - $2,500",
  "description": "<p><strong>Mechanic Needed</strong><br />Salary : $1,800 - $2,200 (OT will be paid accordingly)<br /><br />Allowances :<br />Laundry allowance : $40 per month<br />Night shift allowance : $18/ per night<br />Transport allowance $25 per month<br />Skills allowance : upon confirmation $90<br />Job Description<br /><br />· Ensure proper maintenance of all golf course machinery and equipment.<br />· Maintain mowing equipment, ensuring it's operational and properly sharpened.<br />· Oversee the maintenance of golf cars, turf-mates, and all Club automotive vehicles.<br />· Adhere to Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) and follow safety protocols at all times.<br />· Complete scheduled maintenance tasks within the designated timeframes.<br />· Update repair logs on a daily basis.<br />· Keep work tools and areas clean, organized, and well-maintained.<br />· Perform other duties as assigned by management.<br /><br />Job Requirement<br /><br />Qualifications<br /><br />· NTC 3 or NITEC in Automotive Training<br /><br />Experience<br /><br />· Experience in basic servicing, maintenance, and repairs.<br />· Ability to work early hours (occasionally 4am), including weekends and public holidays. (Transport will be provided)<br /><br />Skills & Knowledge<br /><br />· Basic reading, writing, and arithmetic skills.<br />· Ability to collaborate effectively with staff and other departments.<br />· No experience required; training will be provided for suitable candidates.<br /><br />Interested candidates please call/ WhatsApp me at 88175405 or send your resume to aly@swiftsearchglobal.com<br /><br />Victor Gan (R1550441)<br />Swift Search Global Pte Ltd (EA 18C9495)</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Willie Goh<br />EA Personnel No: R2197853</p>",
